item.title: AP Chemistry Exam Information
item.description: AP Chemistry Exam Exam Date Mon, May 6, 2024 | 12 PM Local Exam Format The AP Chemistry Exam has consistent question types, weighting, and scoring guidelines every year, so you and your students know what to expect on exam day. Starting with the 2023 exam, a scientific or graphing calculator is recommended for use on both sections of the exam. Section I: Multiple Choice 60 Questions | 1 Hour 30 minutes | 50% of Exam Score
